videos.headline: Clair's 43-yard run puts Falcons in red zone
videos.description: Andrew Clair runs for 43 yards to Kent State's 3-yard-line to set Bowling Green up for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Clair delivers Bowling Green's first score of night
videos.description: Andrew Clair rushes for 3 yards into the end zone to give the Falcons an early lead.

videos.headline: Bowling Green makes one-handed interception
videos.description: George Bollas' pass is picked off by Cameron Jefferies and returned for an 8-yard gain.

videos.headline: Doege finds Guyton for 36-yard TD
videos.description: Jarret Doege completes to Datrin Guyton for 36 yards in the end zone to extend the Falcons lead.

videos.headline: Bollas sneaks up the middle for a TD
videos.description: George Bollas guts through the middle for 22 yards into the end zone to put Kent State on the board.

videos.headline: Rankin's 33-yard run puts Golden Flash in red zone
videos.description: Justin Rankin breaks through the middle for a 33-yard gain to the Bowling Green 19-yard-line.

videos.headline: Bowling Green WR makes incredible grab over defenders' head
videos.description: Jarret Doege connects with Teo Redding who makes an amazing catch for a 35-yard gain for the Falcons.

videos.headline: Doege extends Falcons' lead
videos.description: Jarret Doege rushes into the end zone for 1 yard to cushion Bowling Green's lead.

videos.headline: Cleveland's TD pads Bowling Green lead
videos.description: Josh Cleveland runs for a 5-yard TD to extend the Falcons' lead.

videos.headline: Matthews rushes for a 3-yard TD
videos.description: Will Matthews runs for a Kent State touchdown to close the gap on the Falcons.

videos.headline: Doege finds Redding for another Falcons TD
videos.description: Jarret Doege completes a pass to Teo Redding for a seven-yard gain into the end zone.
